Features
♦ This repository displays all Topics posted by the users and the real-time count of posts/answers for that specific topic.
♦ It adds a new topic and its description based on pre-defined/entered categories (saved in the database). Users’ ability to put answers/post and comments to each topic.
♦ User profile page displays how may topics, answers and comments the user has posted.
♦ Contains Login/Logout feature.
